ion. The runner is then returned to the default group.\\n\\nOAuth app tokens and personal access tokens (classic) need the `admin:org` scope to use this endpoint.\",\n      \"parameters\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"org\",\n          \"in\": \"path\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"The organization name. The name is not case sensitive.\",\n          \"type\": \"string\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"runner_group_id\",\n          \"in\": \"path\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Unique identifier of the self-hosted runner group.\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"runner_id\",\n          \"in\": \"path\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Unique identifier of the self-hosted runner.\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"hasRequestBody\": false,\n      \"risk\": \"destructive\",\n      \"cacheable\": false,\n      \"responseCodes\": [\n        \"204\"\n      ],\n      \"inputHints\": {\n        \"path\": [\n          \"org\",\n          \"runner_group_id\",\n          \"runner_id\"\n        ],\n        \"query\": [],\n        \"headers\": [],\n        \"body\": false\n      },\n      \"graphql\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"actions/list-self-hosted-runners-for-org\",\n      \"method\": \"GET\",\n      \"path\": \"/orgs/{org}/actions/runners\",\n      \"tag\": \"actions\",\n      \"summary\": \"List self-hosted runners for an organization\",\n      \"description\": \"Lists all self-hosted runners configured in an organization.\\n\\nAuthenticated users must have admin access to the organization to use this endpoint.\\n\\nOAuth app tokens and personal access tokens (classic) need the `admin:org` scope to use this endpoint. If the repository is private, the `repo` scope is also required.\",\n      \"parameters\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"name\",\n          \"in\": \"quer